Harry Northrup https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harry_Northrup 0 Harry Northrup (31 July 1875 – 2 July 1936) was a French-born American film actor of the silent era. He appeared in 135 films between 1911 and 1935. He was born in Paris and died in Los Angeles, California.
